<H1 ALIGN=CENTER>TECHNOS Quarterly</H1>
<H2 ALIGN=CENTER>For Education and Technology</H2>
<HR>

<H1 ALIGN=CENTER>Biography</H1>

<P><IMG SRC="/journal/bios/mfinch.gif" align=right hspace=10><BR><BR>
<B>Mary-Lee Finch</B> has taught in regular, special, and gifted education positions for more than 25
years. A teacher and campus technology facilitator at Timberwilde Elementary School , she is also training to become an Effective Teacher Practices mentor for the Northside Independent School District in San Antonio.</P>
<BR CLEAR=RIGHT><BR>
