<HR>

<H1 align=center>Biography</H1>
<IMG SRC="/journal/bios/cfrank.gif" hspace=10 align=left>
<P><B>John Kerin</B> is senior vice president of Information Management for The McGraw-Hill Companies. His responsibilities include providing strategic direction for the corporate-wide development of electronically based information products and services and creating policy regarding the company's use of information. <B>Charlotte Frank</B> is vice president of Research & Development for The McGraw-Hill Companies' Educational and Professional Publishing Group. She previously served as executive director of the Division of Curriculum and Instruction at the New York City Board of Education.</P><BR CLEAR=RIGHT>

