<A HREF="/ait/aait.htm"><IMG SRC="/images/aitlogo.gif" ALIGN=RIGHT BORDER=0 HSPACE=0></A>
<A HREF="/technos/atechnos.htm"><IMG SRC="/images/technos/tpress.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER=0 HSPACE=0></A>

<H1 ALIGN=CENTER>TECHNOS Quarterly</H1>
<H2 ALIGN=CENTER>For Education and Technology</H2>
<HR>

<H1 ALIGN=CENTER><I>Biography</I></H1>

<IMG SRC="/journal/bios/rlookatch.gif"align=left hspace=10>
<BR><BR>
<P><B>Richard Lookatch</B> is an educational psychologist with the Agency for Instructional Technology's instructional design unit in Bloomington, Indiana. He received his Ph.D. from the University of Wisconsin and has served the training and education field for 20 years, specializing in educational technologies.</P>
<BR><BR>

