<DOCNO>WT24-B23-53</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA068-000422-B003-186</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.ait.org:80/journal/volume5/sb2meier.htm 206.106.95.11 19970113053209 text/html 6611
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
