<A HREF="/technos/atechnos.htm"><IMG SRC="/images/technos/tpress.gif" ALIGN=LEFT BORDER=0 HSPACE=0></A>
<H1 align=center>TECHNOS Quarterly</H1>
<HR>
<H2 ALIGN=CENTER>Biography</H2>
<BR>
<P><IMG SRC="mnorris.gif" align=left hspace=10><B>Marilyn W. Norris</B>, founder and president of 21st Century Resources, Inc., in Dallas, is a writer and former educator. In 1979 she joined JCPenney as editor of <I>Forum</I> magazine, a publication dedicated to bringing information on trends and issues to educators. Norris, a research manager in Penney's Corporate Planning and Research Department, is president of the Dallas/Fort Worth chapter of The Planning Forum, an international organization of professionals in the field of strategic management and planning.</P>
