<HTML>

<HEAD>

<TITLE>COMMUNITY INVOLVEMENT
</TITLE>

<META NAME="GENERATOR" CONTENT="Internet Assistant for Microsoft Word 2.0z">
</HEAD>

<body text="#001831" link="#001831" vlink="#001831" background="../images/smallicons/Icon_frmbckgrd2.gif">
<p><br>
<center>
<table cellpadding="12" bgcolor="#ffffff" width="600">
<tr>
<td>
<font face="Helvetica" size="6">COMMUNITY INVOLVEMENT</font><br>




	Mann Packing Company believes in contributing to the development of our industry and community. We currently support:
<p>
	Ag In The Classroom, Alisal High School, Alisal Youth Football, American Cancer Society, American Heart Association, California Agricultural Leadership Program, Big Brothers/Big Sisters, California International Airshow, California Rodeo, California Women for Agriculture, Central Coast YMCA, Chamber of Commerce, City of Hope, Food Bank for Monterey County, F.O.O.D. Crops, Foundation for Monterey County Libraries, Franciscan Workers (Dorothys Place), Joe Gheen Stag Barbecue, Greenfield Broccoli Festival, Grower-Shipper Golf Tournament (proceeds provide scholarships for children of farm-laborers), Hartnell College Volleyball, Hartnell College Quarterback Club, Kiwanis Club of Salinas, Laguna Seca Rubber Duck Race, Meals on Wheels, Monterey County Boy Scouts, Monterey County Girl Scouts, Monterey County Parks Department, Monterey County Special Olympics, Monterey National Horse Show, the Mule Deer Foundation, Muscular Dystrophy Association, Natividad Medical Foundation, National Fire Safety Council, North Salinas High School Harvest Festival, Palma Athletic Council, Pediatric Aids Association, Produce for Better Health Foundation, Salinas Firefighters Association, Salinas Girls Fast pitch, Salinas High Baseball, Salinas High Football, Salinas Host Lions, Salinas Jaycees, Salinas Police Officers Association, Salinas Soccer League, Salinas Senior Babe Ruth, Salinas Union High School, Salinas Valley Ducks Unlimited, Salinas Valley Fair, Salinas Valley Memorial Hospital, Salinas Valley Quarterback Club, Sansum Medical Research, Second Chance Youth Program, Sober Graduation (Alisal, Gonzales, North High, Salinas High), Taste of the Valley, Tony Theresa Golf Classic, Roman Catholic Diocese of Monterey County, Toro Little League, United Emergency Services, United Way of the Salinas Valley, Womens Crisis Center.
<p>
	Mann Packing Company is happy to support these organizations financially. We are also more than happy to open our doors to the Boy Scouts, United Way, or Second Chance Youth Program, who often ask to speak to our production crews about their activities in our community.
<p>
	We are also proud of our employees who give a great deal of their time and energy as volunteers with many of these fine organizations. We strive to be as supportive as possible when it comes time to gather up volunteers to work shifts at Cherrys Jubilee or to serve our favorite recipes on "Broccoli Day" at the Monterey County Fair.
	<p>
	We have four graduates of Leadership Salinas as members of our staff and we are proud of them - as well as all of our volunteers who work hard to help those organizations currently helping our community.



<p>
</td>
</tr>
</table>
