<HEAD>

<TITLE>CONCLUSION

</TITLE>

<META NAME="GENERATOR" CONTENT="Internet Assistant for Microsoft Word 2.0z">
</HEAD>

<body text="#001831" link="#001831" vlink="#001831" background="../images/smallicons/Icon_frmbckgrd2.gif">
<p><br>
<center>
<table cellpadding="12" bgcolor="#ffffff" width="600">
<tr>
<td>
<font face="Helvetica" size="6">CONCLUSION
</font><br>



	Employees at Mann Packing Company are leaders because they are given the opportunity to do just that - lead.  Mr. Mann, Bill Ramsey and Don Nucci have passed their values on to the employees at Mann Packing and support their employees efforts. Knowing that someone believes in you, and knowing that they believe in what youre doing, makes for a productive, successful company.
<p>
	Mann Packing Company has been conducting business in the Salinas Valley for 55 years. Generations of families have worked for, or are currently working at the company. Thats why were investing now in future generations....because when theyre ready to go to work - were going to be here.



<p>
</td>
</tr>
</table>
