<td>
<center>
<font face="Helvetica" size="6">"Our Pledge"</font>
</center>
<br>

<img src="../images/our_pledge.jpg" align="right">
	"This company has turned into quite a family over these past fifty years. Teamwork is why weve been in business for so long, and teamwork is what will carry us into the future. 
<p>
	We are a proactive company. Our purpose is to be a leader in the fresh vegetable industry by providing a consistent supply of quality fresh vegetables through innovation, research, development, and marketing.
<p>
	This is our responsibility. To our beloved late founder H.W. "Cy" Mann, to our employees, our growers, suppliers, service providers and, foremost, our valued customers.
<p>
	Adherence to quality is our key to success - and your key to to a consistent supply of quality <i>Sunny Shores</i> fresh vegetables. We guarantee it. Depend on Mann."
 <p>
<b>Bill Ramsey, Don Nucci<br>
Co-Chief Executive Officers</b>

