<HTML>

<HEAD>

<TITLE>Production
</TITLE>

<META NAME="GENERATOR" CONTENT="Internet Assistant for Microsoft Word 2.0z">
</HEAD>

<body text="#001831" link="#001831" vlink="#001831" background="../images/smallicons/Icon_frmbckgrd2.gif">
<p><br>
<center>
<table cellpadding="12" bgcolor="#ffffff" width="600">
<tr>
<td>
<font face="Helvetica" size="6">Broccoli Production</font><br>


A quality product begins with a quality team of personnel who are dedicated to producing, packing and shipping the freshest vegetables in the world. Our team here at Mann Packing is our most valuable resource and are dedicated to doing just that.
 <p>
As a pioneer in the production of fresh vegetable portions, Mann Packing operates one of the most advanced and modern fresh processing facilities in the produce industry. This facility, and the employees who work here everyday, will produce over one billion broccoli florettes per year, which provides enough daily requirement of vitamin c for over 100 million people.
<p>
Mann Packing has an extensive, on-site Food Safety and Product Protection Program which is concerned foremost with the <b>elimination</b> of microbiological, chemical and physical contaminants in our food products. Product evaluations are performed from seed to shipment where customer specifications and various quality factors including: size, color, texture and overall appearance are measured. The overall concept of cleanliness and good manufacturing practices are adhered to daily. We currently hold the highest food safety rating in the industry. 
<p>
Here at Mann an emphasis is placed on total quality management systems which are stimulated through safety, wellness and merit programs. Bi-monthly tailgate meetings are held with employees to gather feedback concerning all areas of operations. 
<p>
At Mann our safety goal is production without incident or injury. By raising the health and safety awareness of our employees and creating a positive working environment, we have a team of dedicated employees focus on one thingproducing the most outstanding packs in the fresh vegetable industry.
<p>
Mann is at the forefront in new technology and product development. The utilization of fully automated form and fill machines, metal detectors, and an automated sizing and rinsing system are a few examples of fresh technology at work in Manns operations. 




<p>
</td>
</tr>
</table>
<p>
<center>
<a href="../images/footers/footer.map">
<IMG SRC="../images/footers/farmbutt.gif" ismap border="0"></a>
</center>
</center>

</BODY>

</HTML>
