<HEAD>

<TITLE>cold chain copy</TITLE>

<META NAME="GENERATOR" CONTENT="Internet Assistant for Microsoft Word 2.0z">
</HEAD>

<body text="#001831" link="#001831" vlink="#001831" background="../images/smallicons/Icon_frmbckgrd2.gif">
<p><br>
<center>
<table cellpadding="12" bgcolor="#ffffff" width="600">
<tr>
<td>
<B><FONT face="Helvetica" color="#001831" SIZE=5>Cold Chain</FONT></B>
<P>
<basefont size="4">
To preserve optimum freshness and the highest nutritional value,
our vegetables are kept between 34 and 40 degrees Fahrenheit.
Every step from processing to your supermarket should meet our
temperature standard, creating &quot;The Cold Chain.&quot; <BR>
<br>
  <table width="550" border="0">
  <tr>
  <td>
<basefont size="4">
The product is first hand packed and surrounded with slush ice
for freshness.
  </td>
  <td align="middle"> 
<b>34&#176; - 40&#176;</b> 
  </td>
  <td>
<img src="../images/coldcycle/Packed.jpg">
  </td>
  </tr>


  <tr>
  <td>
<basefont size="4">
Temporarily stored before shipping.
  </td>
  <td align="middle">
  <b>34&#176; &#45; 40&#176;</b>
  </td>
  <td>
<img src="../images/coldcycle/Stored.jpg">
  </td>
  </tr>


  <tr>
  <td>
<basefont size="4">
Loaded onto refrigerated trucks without ever changing temperature.
  </td>
  <td align="middle">
<b>34&#176; - 40&#176;</b>
  </td>
  <td>
<img src="../images/coldcycle/Trucks.jpg">
  </td>
  </tr>


  <tr>
  <td>
<basefont size="4">
Retailer follows our cold chain guidelines when warehousing.
  </td>
<td align="middle">
<b>34&#176; - 40&#176;</b>
  </td>
  <td>
<img src="../images/coldcycle/Retailer.jpg">
  </td>
  </tr>

  <tr>
  <td>
<basefont size="4">
Displayed cold for shoppers.
  </td>
  <td align="middle">
<b>34&#176; - 40&#176;</b>
  </td>
  <td>
<img src="../images/coldcycle/Display.jpg">
  </td>
  </tr>


  <tr>
  <td>
<basefont size="4">
For optimum taste, MANN's fresh-cut vegetables should ideally
be refrigerated within 30 minutes after purchase. 
  </td>
<td align="middle">
<b>34&#176; - 40&#176;</b>
  </td>
  <td>
<img src="../images/coldcycle/Fridge.jpg">
  </td>
  </tr>


  

  <tr>
  <td>

<hr width=250>
  </td>
 <td>

<hr width=150>
  </td>
 <td>

<hr width=150>
  </td>
  </tr>
  </table>
</td>
</tr>
</table>
