<HTML>

<HEAD>

<TITLE>Packaging</TITLE>

<META NAME="GENERATOR" CONTENT="Internet Assistant for Microsoft Word 2.0z">
</HEAD>

<body text="#001831" link="#001831" vlink="#001831" background="../images/smallicons/Icon_frmbckgrd2.gif">
<p><br>
<center>
<table cellpadding="12" bgcolor="#ffffff" width="600">
<tr>
<td>
<B><FONT face="Helvetica" color="#001831" SIZE=6>Packaging</FONT></B>
<P>

  <table width="600" border="0">
  <tr>
<td>
<u><b><FONT color="green" SIZE=4>Grown to Perfection</font></b></u> <br><b>
Mann Packing has an extensive quality control program in farm production. Our team of veteran employees has over 100 years of combined growing experience.  They consult with our growers during every phase of the growing and harvesting process.
</td>
<td>
<img src="../images/coldcycle/Field.JPG">
</td>
<td>
<img src="../images/coldcycle/Team.JPG">
</td>
<td>
<u><b><FONT color="green" SIZE=4>
Our Personal Touch</font></b></u><br><b>
Our team here at Mann Packing is our most valuable resource.  No machine can compare to our highly skilled team of personnel dedicated to producing, packing and shipping the freshest vegetables in the world.
</td>
</tr>
  <tr>
<td valign="top" colspan=2>


<img align="right" src="../images/coldcycle/Inspection.JPG">

<u><b><FONT color="green" SIZE=4>Safety is Number One</font></b></u><b>


<br>


At Mann Packing our extensive, on-site Food Safety and Product Protection Program not only meets all government standards, but we continually perform voluntary audits to ensure that every product is safe and nutritious  In addition, all of our vegetables are hand-cut with sterile, stainless steel knives and individually sorted for quality by our team.  The hand-picked vegetables are then measured in precise protions per package and put through a metal detector to ensure safety.


</td>
<td colspan=2>

<img align="left" src="../images/coldcycle/Breathable.jpg">

<u><B><FONT SIZE=4 color="green">The Revolutionary Breathable Bag</FONT></B></u>
<b>
<br>
The big question has always been, &quot;How can you keep pre-packaged
vegetables fresh without preservatives?&quot;
 Since vegetables
continue to breathe after harvest by taking in oxygen and giving
off carbon dioxide, they will suffocate in an ordinary plastic
bag. After over 15 years of research, a special film was discovered
that revolutionized our industry. This specially designed film
allows MANN's fresh-cut vegetables to breath, keeping them fresh
and preservative free!
  </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
  <td colspan="4"><br>
<font color="green" size="4"><B>Resealing opened fresh-cut vegetables</B>
  </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
  <td colspan="4"><b>
After opening a bag of vegetables, simply seal the freshness in
by twisting the bag closed and adhering a rubber band or twist
tie for a secure hold. Place in the crisper for proper storage.
  </td>
  </tr>

  
  </table>
</td>
</tr>
</table>
