<DOCHDR>
http://broccoli.com:80/institute/nutritionreport.htm 204.157.36.20 19970118212449 text/html 46614
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Microsoft-IIS/2.0
Date: Sat, 18 Jan 1997 21:28:01 GMT
Content-Type: text/html
Accept-Ranges: bytes
Last-Modified: Mon, 26 Aug 1996 23:51:40 GMT
