<CENTER><B>(408) 626-2818</B></CENTER>

<CENTER><B>FAX: (408) 626-2817</center> <BR>

<p>

<img src="../images/REACHFORITLOGO.jpg">  <B><FONT SIZE=5><u>Reach For It!</u></FONT></B>
<br>
The Canadian Produce Marketing Association has an equivalent to the Produce for Better Health's Foundation's 5 A DAY program. It's called REACH FOR IT! and emphasizes a healthy lifestyle of eating 5 to 10 servings of fruits and vegetables, being active, and feeling good about yourself. <BR>

<P>
They have a children's newsletter called, &quot;Mighty Munchers News&quot;, which has fun nutritious ideas and games about fruits and vegetables. Children can write in and join the Mighty Munchers Club. To request a newsletter or for more information please write, e-mail, or fax to:<BR>

<P>
<CENTER><B>Canadian Produce Marketing Association</B></CENTER>

<CENTER><B>The Mighty Munchers </B></CENTER>

<CENTER><B>310-1101 Prince of Wales Drive</B></CENTER>

<CENTER><B>Ottawa ON K2C 3W7</B></CENTER>

