<!-- ************************************************************* -->

<font size="6" color="#004080">The Healthy Diet Diary</font></center>

<!------------------------ Start table one ---------------------------->



<P><b>
A diet diary isn't something you always want to carry around and
obsess over, but it's great when you're staring a new healthy
diet plan to monitor exactly what, when and where you are eating.
You can identify when you become hungry during the day, so in
the future you'll know to bring a healthy snack. You can also
write down your exercise routine to estimate your daily caloric
expenditure. <BR>
<BR>
<BR>

<P>
