<title>MANN Foodservice--Product Descriptions</title>

</head>

<body bgcolor="#FFEBD7">
<center>
<table bgcolor="#ffffff" cellpadding="10" width="600" border="0">
<tr>
<td>

<font color="#000080"><h2>MANN Foodservice--Product Descriptions</h2></font>





<img src="../images/products/brocwokly.jpg" align=right vspace=10 hspace=20>

<ul>
<b><font color="green">Manns Broccoli Wokly</b></font><br>
<li>A random-cut florette with a crown width ranging from 1" to 2 3/4".
<li>Packed 18# loose and iced.
<li>Best foodservice florette value. 
<li>Used in side dishes and soups.
</ul>
<br clear=all>
<p>


<img src="../images/products/gourmet_broc.jpg" align=right vspace=30 hspace=4>

<ul>
<b><font color="green">Manns Gourmet Broccoli Florettes
</b></font><br>
<li>A random cut florette with a crown width ranging from 1" to 2 1/4".
<li>Packed in 4/3# bag cartons, 12/4 oz. portions per bag. and 6/3# bag cartons. 
<li>Iced or iceless. 
<li>We recommend iced unless you can guarantee the consistency of the cold chain. 
<li>Averages 65 bite size buds per pound. 
<li>Used in salad bars and pastas. 
</ul>
<br clear=all>
<p>



<img src="../images/products/pizzacut.jpg" align=right vspace=10 hspace=20>

<ul>
<b><font color="green">Manns Pizza-cut Broccoli Florettes
</b></font><br>
<li>A florette cut with a maximum crown width of 
1 1/4". 
<li>Packed 18# loose and iced, 72/4 oz. portions or in 4/3# bag cartons iced, 12/4 oz. portions per bag. 
<li>Best cut for pizza, excellent cut for pastas.
<br clear=all>
</ul>
<p>


<img src="../images/products/culinarycut.jpg" align=right vspace=10 hspace=20>

<ul>
<b><font color="green">Manns Culinary Cut Florettes
</b></font><br>
<li>A biased-cut florette with a crown width ranging from 2" to 
2 1/2" and a stem length averaging 2 1/4". 
<li>Packed in 4/3# bag cartons iced or iceless, 12/4 oz. portions per bag. 
<li>Best for dips and other appetizers, grilling, oriental dishes, imaginative signature items. 
<li>Available September 1, 1996
</ul>
<br clear=all>
<p>


<img src="../images/products/brocspears.jpg" align=right vspace=10 hspace=20>

<ul>
<b><font color="green">
Manns 3" to 4" Broccoli Spears
</b></font><br>
<li>packed 15# loose, iced, 60/4 oz. portions per carton. 
<li>Best for center of the plate vegetarian entres, side dish accompaniment with cheese sauce or dress, entre salads.
</ul>
<br clear=all>
<p>



<img src="../images/products/supervegmed.jpg" align=right vspace=10 hspace=20>

<ul>
<b><font color="green">
Manns Vegetable Medley (Traditional Foodservice)
</b></font><br>
<li>A combination of broccoli florettes, Cauliettes (cauliflower florettes) and carrots in equal parts. 
<li>Packed in 6/3#  bag cartons, iced, 12/4 oz. portions per bag. 
<li>The traditional foodservice bags contain carrots that are biased cut for a "cut on premise" appearance.
</ul>
<br clear=all>
<p>


<img src="../images/products/vegmed.jpg" align=right vspace=10 hspace=20>

<ul>
<b><font color="green">
Manns Vegetable Medley (Supermarket Deli & Catering)
</b></font><br>
<li>a combination of broccoli florettes, Cauliettes (cauliflower florettes) and carrots in equal parts. 
<li>Packed in 6/3#  bag cartons, iced, 12/4 oz. portions per bag. 
<li>The supermarket deli & catering bags contain baby carrots that are more practical for relish trays and dipping.
</ul>
<br clear=all>
<p>


<img src="../images/products/broccoleslaw.jpg" align=right vspace=10 hspace=20>

<ul>
<b><font color="green">
Manns Broccoli Cole Slaw
</b></font><br>
<li>The original broccoli cole slaw developed by Mann Packing Company in 1992. 
<li>Unequaled for taste, fresh, colorful appearance and shelf life (21 days).
<li>Packed in 2/3# bag cartons and 4/5# bag cartons, iced.
</ul>
<br clear=all>
<p>


<img src="../images/products/heartsbroc.jpg" align=right hspace=40>

<ul>
<b><font color="green">
Manns Hearts of Broccoli
</b></font><br>
<li>The Julienne-cut used for the broccoli slaw. 
<li>Packed in 4/5# bag cartons, iced.
</ul>
<br clear=all>
<p>


<img src="../images/products/cauliettes2.jpg" align=right vspace=10 hspace=20>

<ul>
<b><font color="green">
Manns Cauliettes
</b></font><br>
<li>Packed in 2/3# bag cartons, iced and iceless and 4/3# bag cartons, iced. 
<li>Bite size, random cut cauliflower florettes. 
<li>Best for salads, dips, side dishes.
</ul>
<p>


<ul>
<b><font color="green">
Manns Pizza-cut Cauliettes
</b></font><br>
<li>Packed in 2/3# bag cartons, iced and iceless.  
<li>Small size for pizzas and pasta.
</ul>
<br clear=all>
<p>


<img src="../images/products/rainbow2.jpg" align=right vspace=10 hspace=20>

<ul>
<b><font color="green">
Manns Rainbow Salad
</b></font><br>
<li>Packed in 9/1# bag cartons, iced.
<li>A combination of approximately 40% shredded Hearts of Broccoli, 40% shredded cauliflower, 10% shredded carrots and 10% shredded red cabbage. 
<li>A monotony breaker for salad bars and side dish salads. 
<li>An eye-appealing garnish for traditional sandwiches or a unique ingredients for pita sandwiches.
</ul>
<br clear=all>
<p>


<img src="../images/products/spinach.jpg" align=right hspace=20>


<ul>
<b><font color="green">
Manns Fresh Cello Spinach
</b></font><br>
<li>Packed iceless in 4/2.5# bag cartons, this salad spinach is cleaned and trimmed.
</ul>
<p>


<ul>
<b><font color="green">
Manns Fresh Cello Spinach (Stemless)
</b></font><br>
<li>Packed iceless in 4/2.5# bag cartons, this salad spinach is cleaned and trimmed.
</ul>
<br clear=all>
<p>

<hr>

