  <td>
  <font size=5 color="#001831">
  <b>BROCCOLI WOKLY&reg; STIR FRY</b><BR></FONT><br>
  <font color="#001831" size=4> <b>Fresh-Cut, ready-to-cook</b></font><br>
 <font color="#001831" size=2>
  Now take full advantage of the increasing popularity of Asian Cuisine using <i>fresh-cut</i> vegetable without the downside of lengthy prep time. AAdd chicken, beef, pork or shrimp and serve an an entree. Or add tofu and chopped red or green pepper and serve as a vegetarian entree. Add Oyster Sause and sprinkle with Five Orental Spices and you've gota high-margin signature side dish. Or blanch, chill and serve with crispy oriental noodles as a lunch or dinner salad.
  <p>
  
<i>Another</i> innovation from <b>MANN Foodservice,</b>Mann's Broccoli Wokly&reg; Stir Fry is a mix of approximately 45% fresh borccoli florettes, 25% fresh cauliflower florettes, 15% baby carrots and 15% stringless Sugar Snap&reg; peas.
</font><p>
<font color="#001831" size=5>
