  <td>
  <font size=5 color="red">
  <b>VEGETABLE MEDLEY</b><BR></FONT><br>
  <font color="red" size=4> <b>Fresh-Cut, ready-to-cook</b></font><br>
 <font color="red" size=2>
  Here is your basic American Mixed vegetable dish blended to give you an optimal variety of uses with minimal labor costs and no waste. Multi-use for lunch, dinner, bar/lounge appetizers and catered events. Serve raw or lightly blanched with vegetable, onion, ranch and blue cheese dips.
  <p>
  Serve as value-added garnish with Buffalo Wings, fried calamari, chicken tenders, etc. Use as main vegetable ingredient for Pasta Primavera, as signature Italian side dish, buttered and sprinkled with fresh/dry oregano or fine herbs. Or use as tradtional vegetable side dish, as base filling for vegetable pot pie dressing, or steam lightly and serve with dressing or low-cal yogurt sauce as a veggie entree.
  <p>
  
<i>Another</i> innovation from <b>MANN Foodservice,</b> Mann's Vegetable Medley is a mix of approximately 34% fresh broccoli flotettes, 33% cauliflower florettes and 33% carrots.
</font><p>
<font color="red" size=5>
<b>For more information call:<br>1(800)884-MANN</font><p>
