<p>Keep dry
<p>Rotate first in, first out

</FONT>
  </td>
  <td valign="top">
  <font SIZE=2 color="#000000">
Lunch and dinner day parts as appetizer with dips or veggie salad. Can serve as base for Italian and Asian side dishes, as steamed vegetarian entree with rice or potatoes and sprinkled with blanched almond slices, as labor saving, high flavor addition to stews or as topping with pasta</FONT>
  </td>
  <td valign="top">
  <font SIZE=2 color="#000000">
 Processed under HACCP guidelines with AIB certification<p>
 100% usable product<p>
 No additives<p>
 Year-round availability<p>
 Year-round stable pricing</FONT>
  </td>
  <td valign="top">
  <font SIZE=2 color="#000000">
  Dramatically lower prep costs<p>
  Mix aimed at optimal 14 day shelf life<p>
  On-trend with today's ethnic menuing<p>
  Serve either cooked or raw
</FONT>
  </td>
  </tr>
  </table>
</td>
