<head>
<!-- MANN'S FOOD SERVICE, authored by gavdw on 7/9/96  -->
<!--  Last Edited 11 JUL 96 by Mark Dreessen  -->
<title>Broccoli Coleslaw</title>

</head>

<body bgcolor="#ffffff">
<center>
<table border="0" width="640" cellspacing=0 cellpadding=0>
<tr>
<td colspan="2">

  <table cellpadding="10" cellspacing=0 bgcolor="#001831" border="0" width="630">
  <tr>
  <td>
  <font size="10" color="#ffb900">
  <b>MANN FOODSERVICE</b><BR></FONT>
  <FONT SIZE="6" COLOR="#ffb900">
  Fresh-Cut Vegetables
  </td>
  </tr>
  </table>

</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td valign=top>
  <table cellpadding="10" cellspacing=0 bgcolor="#ffb900" border="0" width="345">
  <tr>
  <td>
  <font color="#001831" size=5 color="#000000">
  <b>BROCCOLI COLESLAW</b><BR></FONT><br>
  <font color="#001831" size=4> <b>Fresh-Cut, ready-to-serve</b></font><br>
 <font color="#001831" size=2>
  Experience the incredible number of uses for MANN's Broccoli Cole Slaw.  Serve it in a breakfast omelet or a take-out burrito.  Substitute it for lettuce in a taco or in a submarine sandwich.  Use it as a topping for baked potatoes, as a stir fry or as a relish for hamburgers, hot dogs or sausages.  As a classic cole slaw, either on-premises or as a take-out, dress it with a poppyseed or Honey-Mustard dressing and chill it for 30 minutes before serving.  Nutritious, innovative and usable in ethnic menu items from stir frys to tostadas to pizzas.
  <p>
A mix of Hearts of Broccoli&#174, carrots and red cabbage from MANN'S Foodservice gives you a menuing edge on your competition.
<p>
Treat your customers to a new fresh food experience.<br>
<i>Another</i> innovation from <b>MANN Foodservice.</b>
</font><p>
<font color="#001831" size=5>
<b>For more information call:<br>1(800)884-MANN</font><p>
<font size=1> 
<i>Heart's of Broccoli is a registered trademark of Mann Packing Company. Inc.</i></font><br><br>

