<font size="7" color="#004080">Recipe Contest</font></center><font color="red">

<b><font size="4">


What's that great smell coming from your kitchen!?  How about entering your favorite recipes in our recipe contest!  
It's your chance to turn your broccoli ideas and delectable dishes into prizes.  
If your recipe is chosen as this month's winner, you'll receive a Mann gift pack which will include a Mann apron, pot holder, coffee mug, coupons andother goodies! 
It's simple, just follow the rules.<br><a href="fscontestrules.htm">Click here to view Contest Rules</a><br>Good luck and we look forward to hearing from you soon.<br>This month's recipe category is <font size="5" color="green">Broccoli w/ Chicken</font>.

<br><a href="fsrecipecontestform.htm">Click here to fill out the Recipe Contest Entry Form.</a>

<p><a href="fsrecipecontestwinners.htm">Click here to see the Recipe Contest Winners Hall of Fame.</a>

</b>


