http://broccoli.com:80/kitchen/kids_broccoli_recipes.htm 204.157.36.20 19970118214505 text/html 14302
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Microsoft-IIS/2.0
Date: Sat, 18 Jan 1997 21:48:15 GMT
