<td valign=top><font color="green" FACE="Helvetica"><h2>"Detachable Harvesting Machines"</h2></font>
<font color="#ffffff">
Detachable harvesting machines used in the 1970s and early 1980s. Harvesting equipment was hooked to trucks for transport. The large belts over the truck bed would feed the harvested broccoli into bins for transport to the packing facility.

