<head>
<title>Introduction</title>

</head>



<body link="4A52B5" vlink="CE7B63" bgcolor="#000000">

<FONT SIZE=2> 



<table border="0" width="100%">
<tr>
<td valign=top>
<img src="../images/vtour/photo43sm.jpeg">
</td>

<td valign=top><font color="green" FACE="Helvetica"><h2>"Broccoli Harvesting Machines"</h2></font>
<font color="#ffffff">
Like a phantom surfboard across a sea of green, broccoli harvesting machines and the crews operating them will pass through broccoli fields three different times (on average). Broccoli plants grow a number of shoots, not at the same rate. Usually growers will wait a week to ten days before going back into a field for an additional cutting. 
</font>

</td>
</tr>
</table>
