<head>
<title>Introduction</title>

</head>



<body link="4A52B5" vlink="CE7B63" bgcolor="#000000">

<FONT SIZE=2> 



<table border="0" width="100%">
<tr>
<td valign=top>
<img src="../images/vtour/photo40bg.jpeg">
</td>

<td><font color="green" FACE="Helvetica"><h2>"Traditional Bunched Broccoli"</h2></font>
<font color="#ffffff">
Today, traditional "bunched" broccoli which can be found in the store with a rubber band around it, is packed in the field, not packing sheds. These crew members are cutting the stalks which will be gathered, bunched and packed in one swift process.

</font>


</td>
</tr>
