<html>
<head>
<title>Introduction</title>

</head>



<body link="4A52B5" vlink="CE7B63" bgcolor="#000000">

<FONT SIZE=2> 



<table width="100%" border="0">
<tr>
<td valign=top>

<img src="../images/vtour/photo41bg.jpeg">
</td>

<td><font color="green" FACE="Helvetica"><h2>"Compact, Hydraulic Machines"</h2></font>
<font color="#ffffff">
Compact, hydraulic machines have replaced the traditional bunching machines that used twist ties. Today, rubber bands are wrapped around three to four stalks of broccoli with hydraulics. The invention of this portable machine made the broccoli packing houses obsolete and caused an influx of competition from growers that could not previously pack broccoli due to the lack of a packing facility.

</font>


</td>
</tr>
</table>
</body>
