  <td><font face="Helvetica" size="3">

<font color="green"><b>
 Broccoli Wokly Pizza</b></font>
<p>



YIELD 2-4 Servings
<p>
<img align="right" src="../../images/foodshots/BRWOKLYPIZZA.jpg">
1 large 	Boboli bread<br>
2 cups 	<b>Broccoli Wokly florettes</b>, chopped and blanched<br>
8 oz.		Commercial or home made pizza sauce<br>
1 Tbs.	Olive Oil<br>
1 Tbs.	Fresh Garlic, chopped<br>
1 cup		Shredded Mozzarella cheese (may add more or less if desired)
	<p>
