<font color="green"><b>
Creamy Broccoli Slaw</b></font>
<p>


Serves 8
<p>
1		can (10 1/4 oz.) Campbells condensed cream, of celery soup<br>
1/3	cup of mayonnaise<br>
1/3	cup of cider vinegar<br>
2 		Tablespoons of sugar<br>
1 		Tablespoon of prepared mustard<br>
1		teaspoon of celery seed (optional)<br>
1/2 	teaspoon of pepper<br>
1		bag of <b>Manns Broccoli Cole Slaw</b> <br>
<p>
1. Mix soup, mayonnaise, vinegar, sugar, mustard, celery seed, and pepper.
 <p>
2. Toss cole slaw and soup mixture until evenly coated. Refrigerate 1 hour.



