  <tr>
  <td><font face="Helvetica" size="3">

<font color="green"><b>
Easy Chicken & Biscuits </b></font>
<p>




Serves 5
<p>
1 		can (10 1/4 oz.) Campbells condensed cream of celery soup<br>
1 		can (10 1/4 oz.) Campbells condensed cream of potato soup<br>
1		cup of milk<br>
1/4 	teaspoon of crushed dry thyme leaves<br>
1/4	teaspoon of pepper<br>
1 		bag (16 oz.) of <b>Manns Broccoli & Carrots</b>, cooked and drained<br>
2		cups of cubed, cooked chicken<br>
1		package (7 1/2 or 10 oz.) refrigerated biscuits
<p>
1. In a 3 quart shallow baking dish, mix the soups, milk, thyme, pepper,. broccoli, carrots and chicken
<p>
2. Bake at 400 F. 15 minutes or until hot. Stir. Arrange biscuits over chicken. Bake 14 minutes or until the biscuits are golden.




