  <tr>
  <td><font face="Helvetica" size="3">

<font color="green"><b>
Summer Slaw</b></font>
<p>





8-10 Servings
<p>
1 lb.			<b>Manns Broccoli Cole Slaw</b><br>
2 cups			Pineapple chunks<br>
1/2 cup		Almonds, sliced*<br>
2 cups			Apples, diced or sliced<br>
1 cup			Poppy seed dressing<br>
1/2 cup		Raisins (optional)<br>
1 cup			Pears (optional)
<p>
1. In a suitable size mixing bowl, add broccoli cole slaw, pineapple, almonds, apples, pears and raisins (if optioned).  Add poppy seed dressing and blend thoroughly.
 <p>
2. *Please note:  Sunflower seeds may be substituted for almonds.

