<!-----------------------------Keywords------------------------->

<!--

Mealtime Lunch Dinner 
Region Japan
Kids
Product Mann's Broccoli Wokly Stir Fry 
Prep time 3 4 minutes

-->

<!---------------------------End Keywords----------------------->



<body text="#000000" vlink="green" link="#6A006A" bgcolor="#FFEBD7"><center>
<font face="Helvetica" size="7" color="#6A006A">
 Easy Asian Stir Fry
</font>

<table width="600" border="0">
<tr>
<td>

  


<!----------------#2------------------------>
  <table bgcolor="#FFFFFF" border="1" bordercolor="#808040" cellpadding="7">
  <tr>
  <td><font face="Helvetica">
<center>
   <table cellspacing="12" border="0" bgcolor="#FFFFFF">
   <tr>
   <td colspan="2">
<font face="Helvetica" color="green"><b>
MANNS Easy Asian Stir Fry

</b></font>
   </td>
   </tr>
   <tr>

<p>
<td valign="top"><font face="Helvetica">
	<nobr><b>100 (4 oz.) Servings 	</b></nobr><br>
	4.25 cups	<br>
	25 lbs.	<br>
	5 cups	<br>
   </td>
   <td valign="top"><font face="Helvetica">
<b>Ingredients</b><br>
Vegetable oil<br>
Manns Broccoli Wokly Stir Fry 	<br>
Prepared stir fry sauce or <br>spicy 
Szechwan-style sauce

   </td>
	
		



   </tr>
   </table>
</center>

<p>

<b>PROCEDURE:</b><br>
1. For individual service:  heat 2 tsp. vegetable oil in wok, skillet or on flat grill.  
 <p>
2. Add 4 oz. (1 cup) Stir Fry Vegetables and cook for 2 minutes while tossing vegetables until broccoli turns bright green.
 <p>
3. Add 2 tsp. sauce and continue to stir fry another 30 to 60 seconds until vegetables are glazed, but still crisp.


<p>
<u><b>Nutrients Per Serving</b></u></font><pre>
Calories:	504	Vitamin A:	678 IU
