	1-1/2 Tbs.	<br>
	25 lbs.	

   </td>
   <td valign="top"><font face="Helvetica">
<b>Ingredients</b><br>
Prepared teriyaki glaze<br>
Vegetable oil<br>
Ground ginger<br>
Manns Vegetable Medley

   </td>
	

 
   </tr>
   </table>
</center>

<p>

<b>PROCEDURE:</b><br>
1. In large bowl, combine teriyaki glaze, vegetable oil and ginger; stir to blend.
 <p>
2. Evenly distribute Vegetable Medley in hotel pans; pour seasoned glaze over vegetables and toss to coat.
 <p>
3. Bake uncovered in preheated 375F oven, until vegetables are cooked but still tender, about 12 to 15 minutes, stirring once during cooking.





 
