<!--

Mealtime Lunch Dinner 
Region California
Kids
Product Mann's Vegetable Medley

-->

<!---------------------------End Keywords----------------------->


<body text="#000000" vlink="green" link="#6A006A" bgcolor="#FFEBD7"><center>
<font face="Helvetica" size="7" color="#6A006A">
 California Roasted Vegetables</font>

<table width="600" border="0">
<tr>
<td>

  


<!----------------#2------------------------>
  <table bgcolor="#FFFFFF" border="1" bordercolor="#808040" cellpadding="7">
  <tr>
  <td><font face="Helvetica">
<center>
   <table cellspacing="12" border="0" bgcolor="#FFFFFF">
   <tr>
   <td colspan="2">
<font face="Helvetica" color="green"><b>
MANNS California Roasted Vegetables</b></font>
   </td>
   </tr>
   <tr>

<p>
<td valign="top"><font face="Helvetica">
	<nobr><b>100 (3 oz.) Servings </b></nobr><br>
	2.75 lbs./42 oz.	<br>
	3/4 cup	<br>
	1-1/2 oz.	<br>
	3 Tbs.	<br>
	1/2 tsp.	<br>
	25 lbs.	

   </td>
   <td valign="top"><font face="Helvetica">
<b>Ingredients</b><br>
Butter, melted<br>
	Dried parsley flakes<br>
Minced garlic<br>
Salt<br>
Ground pepper<br>
Manns Vegetable Medley
   </td>
	

 
   </tr>
   </table>
</center>

<p>

<b>PROCEDURE:</b><br>
1. In large bowl, combine melted butter, parsley, garlic, salt and pepper; stir to blend.
 <p>
2. Evenly distribute Vegetable Medley in hotel pans; pour seasoned butter mixture over vegetables and toss to coat.
 <p>
3. Bake uncovered in preheated 375F oven, until vegetables are cooked but still tender, about 12 to 15 minutes, stirring once during cooking.
 


 
<p>
<u><b>Nutrients Per Serving</b></u></font><pre>
Calories:	123	Vitamin A:	1213 IU
Protein:	2.5 G	Vitamin C:	69 mg
Carbohydrates:	8 G	Thiamin:	0.1 mg
Dietary Fiber:	3 G	Riboflavin: 	0.1 mg
Fat-total:	9.9 G	Niacin:		0.9 mg
Saturated fat	6 G	Calcium:	47 mg
Cholesterol:	26 mg	Iron:		0.9 mg
Sodium:		321 mg	Cal. from Fat:	68 %
</pre>
  </td>
  </tr>
  </table>

</td>
</tr>
</table>
