<b>PROCEDURE:</b><br>
1. In large container, combine hummus with Broccoli Cole Slaw and jalapeos.
 <p>
2. Split each pita half open and fill with 1/2 cup (4 ounce) scoop of broccoli-hummus mixture and two slices of fresh tomato.
 <p>
3. Line sandwiches open end up in hotel pan, cover with plastic wrap and chill until service.  Sandwiches can also be individually wrapped for "to go" service. 1/2 Pita = 1 Serving
<p>
