-->

<!---------------------------End Keywords----------------------->


<body text="#000000" vlink="green" link="#6A006A" bgcolor="#FFEBD7"><center>
<font face="Helvetica" size="7" color="#6A006A">
 Grab-N-Go Acapulco Broccoli Wrap
</font>

<table width="600" border="0">
<tr>
<td>

  


<!----------------#2------------------------>
  <table bgcolor="#FFFFFF" border="1" bordercolor="#808040" cellpadding="7">
  <tr>
  <td><font face="Helvetica">
<center>
   <table cellspacing="12" border="0" bgcolor="#FFFFFF">
   <tr>
   <td colspan="2">
<font face="Helvetica" color="green"><b>
MANNS Grab-N-Go Acapulco Broccoli Wrap
</b></font>
   </td>
   </tr>
   <tr>

<p>
<td valign="top"><font face="Helvetica">
	<nobr><b>100 Servings 	</b></nobr><br>
	6.25 lbs.	<br>
	12.5 lbs.	<br>
-<br>
	6.25 lbs.	<br>
	3 lbs.	<br>
	1.5 lbs./3 cups	<br>
	100 count	

   </td>
   <td valign="top"><font face="Helvetica">
<b>Ingredients</b><br>
Manns Pizza Cut Broccoli, blanched<br>
Cooked ground beef or turkey, cooked <br>
		with 2 Tbs. taco seasoning blend<br>
Manns Broccoli Cole Slaw<br>
Shredded sharp cheddar cheese<br>
Sour cream<br>
Flour tortillas (9 or 10-inch)
   </td>
	



   </tr>
   </table>
</center>

<p>

<b>PROCEDURE:</b><br>
1. In large container, combine Pizza Cut Broccoli, seasoned ground beef or turkey, Broccoli Cole Slaw, cheese and sour cream; toss.
 <p>
2. To assemble wraps, warm tortillas on flat grill and place 2/3 cup of warm filling down the center of each tortilla, fold in the left and right side of tortilla over filling and roll away from you to close.
 <p>
3. Hold wraps in a warming bin or steam table pans.  Wraps can be enclosed in foil or paper for "to go" service.








<p>
<u><b>Nutrients Per Serving</b></u></font><pre>
