   <tr>

<p>
<td valign="top"><font face="Helvetica">
	<nobr><b>100 Servings 	</b></nobr><br>
	12.5 lbs.	<br>
	4 lbs.	<br>
	1 gallon	<br>
	1 pound	<br>
	2 cups <br>	
