<b>PROCEDURE:</b><br>
1. In large container, combine tuna, Pizza Cut Broccoli, tartar sauce, green onion, celery and lemon juice, and toss.
 <p>
2. To assemble wraps, warm tortillas on flat grill and place 1/2 cup of filling down the center of each tortilla, fold in the left and right side of tortilla over filling and roll away from you to close.  Chill wraps until ready to serve.  Wraps can be enclosed in foil or paper for "to go" service.





