</head>

<body text="#000000" vlink="green" link="#6A006A" bgcolor="#FFEBD7"><center>
<font face="Helvetica" size="7" color="#6A006A">
 Broccoli Wokly Stir Fry with Chili-Orange Sauce
</font>

<table width="600" border="0">
<tr>
<td>

  


<!----------------#2------------------------>
  <table bgcolor="#FFFFFF" border="1" bordercolor="#808040" cellpadding="7">
  <tr>
  <td><font face="Helvetica">
<center>
   <table cellspacing="12" border="0" bgcolor="#FFFFFF">
   <tr>
   <td colspan="2">
<font face="Helvetica" color="green"><b>
MANNS Broccoli Wokly Stir Fry with Chili-Orange Sauce
</b></font>
   </td>
   </tr>
   <tr>

<p>
<td valign="top"><font face="Helvetica">
	<nobr><b>48 Servings	</b></nobr><br>
	3 cups	<br>
	1/4 cup	<br>
	1/2 cup<br>
	1/2 cup	<br>
	4 1/2 lbs.	<br>
	18 lbs.	<br>
	3 lbs.	<br>
	3 lbs.	
   </td>

   <td valign="top"><font face="Helvetica">
<b>Ingredients</b><br>
Peanut or corn oil<br>
Salt (Kosher), coarse<br>
	Garlic, minced<br>
Fresh ginger root, minced<br>
Onion, cut into wedges 1/2" thick<br>
Manns Broccoli Wokly Stir Fry<br>
Red Bell Pepper, cut into 3/4" squares<br>
Water chestnuts, sliced<br>
		Rice, cooked (optional)
   </td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>
<font face="Helvetica" color="green"><b>Chili-Orange Sauce</b></font>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td valign="top"><font face="Helvetica">

	2 qts.	<br>
1 1/2 cups	<br>
1 1/3 cups	<br>
1/2 cup	<br>
1/2 cup	<br>
8 tsp.	<br>
8 tsp.	<br>
2 tsp.	<br>
1 tsp.	<br>
1/4 tsp.	
   </td>

   <td valign="top"><font face="Helvetica">
Chicken broth<br>
Orange juice<br>
Soy Sauce<br>
Sugar<br>
Cornstarch<br>
Orange zest, grated<br>
Balsamic vinegar<br>
Red chili flakes<br>
Asian sesame oil<br>
Salt
   </td>


   </tr>
   </table>
Whisk all ingredients together until well-blended.  Stir again before serving.
</center>

<p>

<u><b>PROCEDURES:</b></u><br>
1. For each serving, heat 1 Tbs. of oil over high heat.<p>
2. Add 1/4 tsp. coarse salt, 1/2 tsp. garlic, 1/2 tsp. ginger and stir fry until fragrant -about 30 seconds.<p>
3. Add 1 1/2 oz. onion (about 1/2 cup) and stir fry for 1 minute.  Add 2 cups of Manns Broccoli Wokly Stir Fry, 1 oz. (about 1/4 cup) of red bell pepper, and 1 oz. (about 1/8 cup) of water chestnuts, stir fry until vegetables are crisp-tender (1 to 2 minutes).<p>
4. Add 2 oz. (1/4 cup) Chili-Orange Sauce and bring to a boil, stirring and tossing until sauce is slightly thickened (30 seconds to 1 minutes).<p>
5. Remove from heat and serve over rice.








<p>
<u><b>Nutrients Per Serving</b></u></font><pre>
(not including rice)
Calories:	255
Protein:	8.41 G
Carbohydrate:	27.9 G
Dietary Fiber:	6.4 G
Fat-total	14.4 G
Cholesterol:	.17 mg
Sodium:		1205 mg
</pre>
  </td>
  </tr>
  </table>

</td>
</tr>
</table>
