<!---------------------------End Keywords----------------------->


<body text="#000000" vlink="green" link="#6A006A" bgcolor="#FFEBD7"><center>
<font face="Helvetica" size="7" color="#6A006A">
  Broccoli Pasta Primavera with Caesar Dressing

</font>

<table width="600" border="0">
<tr>
<td>

  


<!----------------#2------------------------>
  <table bgcolor="#FFFFFF" border="1" bordercolor="#808040" cellpadding="7">
  <tr>
  <td><font face="Helvetica">
<center>
   <table cellspacing="12" border="0" bgcolor="#FFFFFF">
   <tr>
   <td colspan="3">
<font face="Helvetica" color="green"><b>
MANNS Broccoli Pasta Primavera with Caesar Dressing

</b></font>
   </td>
   </tr>
   <tr>

<p>
<td valign="top"><font face="Helvetica">
	<nobr><b>8-12 Servings	</b></nobr><br>
1 lb.	<br>
1 lb.	<br>	
-<br>
2 oz.	<br>
-<br>
1 oz.	<br>
-<br>
4 oz.	<br>	
-<br>
-<br>
4 oz.	<br>
-<br>
-<br>
2 oz.	<br>
-<br>
1 1/2 cups		


</td>
<td valign="top"><font face="Helvetica">
	<nobr><b>50 Servings</b></nobr><br>
	5 lbs.	<br>
5 lbs.<br>
-<br>
10 oz.	<br>
-<br>
5 oz.	<br>
-<br>
1 1/4 lbs.<br>
-<br>
-<br>
1 1/4 lbs.	<br>
-<br>
-<br>
10 oz.	<br>
-<br>
2 qts.
   </td>




   <td valign="top"><font face="Helvetica">
<b>Ingredients</b><br>
Manns Broccoli Wokly<br>
Cooked Rotelli Noodles, chilled, <br>well
		drained<br>
Red skinned onion, peeled, cored, <br>
		julienne sliced 1/8" x 1" long<br>
Green onion, trimmed, green tops only, <br>
		sliced 1/4" long<br>
Fresh zucchini squash, ends trimmed,<br>
		halved lengthwise, sliced into 1/8" thick, <br>
		"crescents"<br>
Fresh yellow squash, ends trimmed,<br>
		halved lengthwise, sliced into 1/8" thick <br>
		"crescents"<br>
Red Bell Pepper, stemmed and seeded, <br>
		julienne cut 1/8" x 1" long<br>
Caesar salad dressing, prepared or <br>
		purchased, chilled, well-mixed
   </td>






   </tr>
   </table>
</center>
<font face="Helvetica">
<p>

<b>PROCEDURE:</b><br>
1. Place cooked, chilled noodles and all of the vegetables in a suitable size mixing container.  Gently toss the ingredients to thoroughly blend together.
 <p>
2. Pour the dressing over the salad ingredients and gently toss together, evenly and completely coating all vegetables and noodles with dressing.
 <p>
3. All the salad to chill for 1 hour prior to serving.
</font></font><br>
<i>Optional:  Prior to serving, sprinkle grated Parmesan cheese evenly over the salad.</i>
<font face="Helvetica">




<p>
<u><b>Nutrients Per Serving</b></u></font></font><pre>
Calories:	212
Fat-total:	14.1 G
Protein:	6.7 G
Cholesterol:	49.9 G
Carbohydrate:	16.2 G
Sodium:		292 mg
Dietary Fiber:	3.08 G
 </pre>
  </td>
  </tr>
  </table>

</td>
</tr>
</table>
