<tr>
<td align="center">


<!-- ************************************************************* -->
<font size="7" color="#004080">Recipe Contest Rules</font>
</center><font color="red"><b><p>



1.      All entrants must be over the age of 21 years.<p>
2.      Recipe becomes the property of Mann Packing Company. Mann Packing
reserves the
right to edit and publish all recipes without compensation, either
in its own publications or in newspapers, magazines or electronic
media.
<p>3.      Recipe must include serving size.
<p>4.      Judging will be based on originality and taste.
<p>5.      No purchase is required. Entries must be received by the 15th of the
        month for qualification and category should be identified. Winners
announced the last day of each
        month at broccoli.com. Recipes should be marked: Recipe Contest
        and sent via e-mail, fax (408) 422-5171 or mail to Mann Packing
        Co.,Inc. Recipe Contest, P.O. Box 690, Salinas, CA 93902-0690
<p>6.      Employees of Mann Packing Company and their affiliated agencies,
        customers or vendors are not eligible.
<p>7.      Void were prohibited by law.


<p>
</td></tr></table><p>




