These figures show the number of suspect cases referred to the CJD surveillance unit in
Edinburgh up until end September 1996 and the number of confirmed cases of sporadic,
familial and iatrogenic definite and probable CJD and GSS for the last full year available. Full
details of our statistics to August 1995 can be found in our fourth annual report. 
