<CENTER><H4><A NAME="International">International</A> Symposium on Spongiform Encephalopathies:<BR>
Generating Rational Policy in the Face of Public Fears</H4></CENTER>
<PRE>Georgetown University <B><FONT COLOR="FF3366">December 12-13, 1996</FONT></B>
The Ceres Forum of the Center for Food and Nutrition Policy at Georgetown University
The American Association of  Veterinary Medical Colleges</PRE>

