Science Keynote Address <FONT COLOR="FF3366">Leavey Ctr, 12:30-1:15 pm</FONT>
        <B>Stanley Prusiner</B>, Univ of California-San Francisco 

Assuring Public Health and Communicating with the Public <FONT COLOR="FF3366">Gaston Hall, 1:45-3:45 pm</FONT>
         Moderator:  <B>Gerald Gaull</B>, Georgetown Center for Food & Nutrition Policy
                <B>David Murray</B>, Statistical Assessment Service - "The impact of the press on public opinion"
